contentrichtext.text: {{Primarysources|date=January 2007}} '''Queenscliff Music Festival''' is a live music festival held in the town of Queenscliff, located on the Bellarine Peninsula, [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]], [[Australia]]. The festival began in 1997 and is held annually on the last weekend of November. == External links == * [http://www.qmf.net.au Queenscliff Music Festival Official Site] * [http://photos.timchuma.com/QMF2005/index.htm 2005 festival photos] * [http://photos.timchuma.com/QMF2006/index.htm 2006 festival photos] {{coord|38|15|52|S|144|39|49|E|region:AU-VIC_type:landmark|display=title}} [[Category:Recurring events established in 1997]] [[Category:Music festivals in Australia]] [[Category:Festivals in Victoria (Australia)]] [[Category:Bellarine Peninsula]] [[Category:1997 establishments in Australia]] {{music-festival-stub}}
